setUpTestData

public static void setUpTestData()
Creates an instance of RoutingGraph to run the tests. The Graph has the following edges (start -> end|weight): 0 -> 2|1; 1 -> 0|2; 1 -> 2|3; 1 -> 3|1.2; 1 -> 4|1.5; 2 -> 0|1; 2 -> 1|3; 2 -> 3|1; 3 -> 1|1.2; 3 -> 2|1; 4 -> 1|1.5; 4 -> 3|2.5; This concludes the following arrays: vertices: {0, 1, 5, 8, 10, 12, 12} edges: {2, 0, 2, 3, 4, 0, 1, 3, 1, 2, 1, 3} weights: {1, 2, 3, 1.2, 1.5, 1, 3, 1, 1.2, 1, 1.5, 2.5} MapPositions: { (1|0|1), (1|2|1), (0|0|1), (0|2|1), (1.5|2.5|1), (1.5|2.5|2) } (longitude | latitude | MapID) Note: There is no dependency between MapPositions and weights.
